@31105     = ~Entangle~
@32105     = ~Entangle
(Transmutation) 
Level: Drd 1, Rgr 1
Range: Sight of Caster
Duration: 10 rounds 
Casting Time: 4
Area of Effect: 20-foot radius
Saving Throw: Reflex partial

When an Entangle spell is cast, it must be cast outside, otherwise it will not work and the spell is wasted. It causes vines to sprout forth from the ground to wrap, twist, and entwine any creatures in the area of effect, preventing movement. Creatures must make a Reflex save every round in order to move through the entangled area. Entangled creatures can still perform normal actions but cannot move and suffer a -2 penalty to Armor Class and attack rolls, as well as a 50% chance of spell failure. All creatures within the area of effect who make their Reflex save move at half rate.~
@31106     = ~Magic Stone~
@32106     = ~Magic Stone
(Enchantment)
Level: Clr 1, Drd 1, Rgr 1
Range: Caster
Duration: 30 rounds or until used up
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

This spell enhances the caster's sling bullets. Any bullet the caster throws will deal magic damage instead of physical damage, and will deal an additional 1d4+1 damage. The spell ends once the caster has thrown a certain number of bullets: five plus one per caster level (maximum of 15 at level 10).~
@31107     = ~Protection from Evil~
@32107     = ~Protection from Evil
(Abjuration) [Good]
Level: Clr 1, Pal 1, Sor/Wiz 1
Range: Touch 
Duration: 1 minute/level
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 1 creature 
Saving Throw: None

This spell forms a magic barrier around the target creature, granting a +2 generic bonus to AC and saving throws against attacks, spells and abilities from evil creatures. In additions, the creature is immune to charm and domination effects. Summoned fiends will not attack their summoner or their summoner's allies if their summoner has Protection from Evil.~
@31115     = ~Armor of Faith~
@32115     = ~Armor of Faith
(Abjuration)
Level: Clr 1, Pal 1, Helm 1
Range: Caster
Duration: 10 rounds + 1 round/level
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None 

The armor of faith is a force of energy that absorbs a portion of the damage intended for the caster. The caster gains a 1/- resistance to all non-poison damage for the duration of the spell. For every five caster levels, they get another 1/- resistance.~
@31117     = ~Frost Fingers~
@32117     = ~Frost Fingers
(Transmutation) 
Level: Drd 1
Range: Caster
Duration: Instantaneous
Casting Time: 1
Area of Effect: 5-foot long, 120 degree arc
Saving Throw: Reflex half

Upon completion of this spell, chilling frost emanates from the caster's hands in the shape of a wedge in front of them.  Any creature caught in the area of effect suffers 1d3 + 1 cold damage per caster level, to a maximum of 1d3 + 10 cold damage.  In addition, the creature is slowed for 2 rounds.  A successful Reflex save halves the damage and negates the slow effect. This spell does not provoke an attack of opportunity.~
@31150     = ~Summon Nature's Ally I~
@32150     = ~Summon Nature's Ally I
(Conjuration) 
Level: Drd 1, Rgr 1
Range: Sight of Caster
Duration: 10 rounds + 5 rounds/level
Casting Time: 6 
Area of Effect: Special 
Saving Throw: None 

This spell summons one or more creatures of nature who will aid the caster for the duration of the spell. The type of creatures that comes is random.~
@31202     = ~Barkskin~
@32202     = ~Barkskin
(Transmutation) 
Level: Drd 2, Rgr 2
Range: Touch
Duration: 10 rounds + 2 rounds/level
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: 1 creature
Saving Throw: None 

Barkskin causes a creature's skin to become as tough as bark, granting a +3 generic AC bonus (+4 at 6th level and +5 at 12th level) for the duration of the spell.~
@31212     = ~Slow Poison~
@32212     = ~Slow Poison
(Conjuration) 
Level: Brd 2, Clr 2, Drd 2, Pal 2, Rgr 1
Range: Touch
Duration: Instantaneous
Casting Time: 0
Area of Effect: 1 creature 
Saving Throw: None

When this spell is placed upon a poisoned individual, it greatly slows the effects of venom, actually neutralizing all but the most deadly poisons.

This spell will also sober up a character that has drunken himself into a stupor.~
@31215     = ~Draw Upon Holy Might~
@32215     = ~Draw Upon Holy Might
(Evocation)
Level: Clr 2, Pal 2, Tempus 2
Range: Caster
Duration: 10 rounds
Casting Time: 5
Area of Effect: Caster
Saving Throw: None

The caster calls upon their god to grant them power for a short period. The caster's Strength, Dexterity and Constitution are all raised by 1 point for every 3 levels of the caster. A third level caster would have their abilities raised by 1, while a 12th level caster would have their abilities raised by 4.

Draw Upon Holy Might is especially effective when cast as a paladin spell. Paladins cast this spell at their full caster level plus 6 (so a 9th-level paladin would have their abilities raised by 5).~
@31226     = ~Moon Motes~
@32226     = ~Moon Motes
(Conjuration) 
Level: Drd 2, Selune 1
Range: Caster
Duration: Instantaneous
Casting Time: 3
Area of Effect: 5' x 20' x 20' cone
Saving Throw: Reflex half

This spell calls upon Selune's connection with moonlight and magic to invoke a spray of glowing spheres. The spell causes 1d6 magic damage per level (max 5d6) to every creature caught in its path. Creatures can make a Reflex save for half damage. This spell does not provoke an attack of opportunity.~
